三、教學目標 Objectives


提升學生在唱歌時的咬字與發音 


Diction/pronunciation skills for singing in English, Italian and Chinese; introduction to phonetic analysis of vocal music in English, Italian and Chinese. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description1.意大利文的正確咬字2.如何正確的應用在歌唱上


●分週敘述 Weekly Schedule





